OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,FCleaner rivers, stronger regulation
OL,7,Fand better accountability for
OL,8,Fpolluters: that's the promise from the
OL,9,FWelsh Government after setting out
OL,10,Fplans to shake up the water industry
OL,11,Fin Wales.
OL,13,FThe proposals include a new regulator
OL,14,Fto keep an eye on prices and rebuild
OL,15,Ftrust with consumers, in what has been
OL,16,Fcalled a "once-in-a-generation reset".
