OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,FSome of the proposals from the Green
OL,7,FPaper include a dedicated Welsh
OL,8,Feconomic regulator for water, better
OL,9,Fmanagement of sewage sludge and
OL,10,Fupgrades to "outdated" infrastructure.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a press conference at
OL,13,FLisvane and Llanishen reservoirs on
OL,14,FTuesday, 3 February, Deputy First
OL,15,FMinister Huw Irranca-Davies said: "Our
OL,16,Fambition is clear and bold: clean and
OL,17,Fthriving rivers, safe and high-quality
OL,18,Fdrinking water, fair and affordable
OL,19,Fservices, and modern infrastructure
OL,20,Fready for the future.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
