OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,F"We will strengthen accountability,
OL,7,Frebuild trust and create a system that
OL,8,Fis simpler, stronger and more
OL,9,Ftransparent.
OL,11,F"Wales now faces an urgent reality.
OL,12,FClimate and nature emergencies, ageing
OL,13,Finfrastructure and public concerns
OL,14,Fabout water quality demand decisive
OL,15,Faction. The system we have today was
OL,16,Fdesigned for a different era. It is
OL,17,Ftime for a fundamental reset."
