OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,FThe proposed changes include
OL,7,Festablishing a new, independent
OL,8,Fregulatory body for Wales to take over
OL,9,Ffunctions currently performed by
OL,10,FOfwat, the economic regulator of the
OL,11,Fwater and wastewater sectors in Wales
OL,12,Fand England, which is set to be
OL,13,Fabolished.
OL,15,FWhile a new body would manage the
OL,16,Findustry's finances and strategy,
OL,17,FNatural Resources Wales - Wales'
OL,18,Fenvironmental regulator - would retain
OL,19,Fits independent role as the dedicated
OL,20,Fenvironmental watchdog responsible for
OL,21,Fmonitoring pollution and river health.
