OL,6,FThe shift would require substantial
OL,7,Ffunding, as well as new legislative
OL,8,Fpowers for the Senedd, meaning the
OL,9,FWelsh Government must first secure the
OL,10,Ftransfer of relevant powers from the
OL,11,FUK Government.
