OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,FIn response to the proposals, Ofwat
OL,7,Finterim CEO Chris Walters said: "This
OL,8,FGreen Paper sets the framework for the
OL,9,Ffuture of the water sector in Wales,
OL,10,Fwhich we welcome. The creation of a
OL,11,Fdedicated regulator for Wales will
OL,12,Fstrengthen scrutiny and accountability
OL,13,Fwithin a framework designed
OL,14,Fspecifically for Wales, marking an
OL,15,Fimportant evolution in how companies
OL,16,Fwill be overseen going forward.
