OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,F"As the Welsh Government develops the
OL,7,Fregulatory new body, we remain
OL,8,Fcommitted to the delivery of our core
OL,9,Ffunctions and are already working
OL,10,Fclosely with Welsh Government, Defra,
OL,11,FNatural Resources Wales and other
OL,12,Fregulators to ensure that the sector
OL,13,Fmoves towards a more integrated and
OL,14,Fresilient future."
