OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,FCommenting on the proposals, Welsh
OL,7,FConservative shadow cabinet secretary
OL,8,Ffor climate change and environment,
OL,9,FJanet Finch-Saunders MS, said: "After
OL,10,F27 years of Plaid Cymru and Labour
OL,11,Fmismanagement, it's hard to believe
OL,12,Fthat by simply creating a new water
OL,13,Fregulator we will suddenly see cleaner
OL,14,Frivers in Wales.
OL,16,F"NRW has been run by Labour since its
OL,17,Fcreation, and it has consistently
OL,18,Ffailed to hold polluters to account.
OL,19,FThat's why I have little confidence
OL,20,Fthat a new regulator, will succeed
OL,21,Fwhere Labour has repeatedly failed.
OL,26,@qD@`OUxD@AOU
