OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F461A1770151267
OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,F"A new regulator won't stop sewage
OL,7,Fspills, won't fix broken
OL,8,Finfrastructure and won't prevent
OL,9,Ffurther water bill rises. The Welsh
OL,10,FConservatives would enforce the law
OL,11,Fproperly, and make polluters pay, not
OL,12,Ffamilies and not the environment."
OL,14,FLeader of the Welsh Liberal Democrats
OL,15,FJane Dodds said: "We're really pleased
OL,16,Fto see it. But it's still not good
OL,17,Fenough, there's still a long way to
OL,18,Fgo. Our rivers and our beaches are
OL,19,Fstill polluted, and it needs
OL,20,Ffundamental reform.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@bO]
