OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F461A1770151267
OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,F"We need total independence, a body
OL,7,Fthat is totally away from the
OL,8,Fgovernment, that has the teeth and the
OL,9,Fpowers we need to ensure that our
OL,10,Frivers and our beaches and rivers are
OL,11,Fmuch cleaner."
OL,13,FDue to the complexity involved in the
OL,14,Ftransition, a new regulatory framework
OL,15,Fis not expected to be fully
OL,16,Foperational until the early 2030s.
OL,18,FThe Future Generations Commissioner
OL,19,Ffor Wales, Derek Walker, said
OL,20,Fimprovements should be made "urgently".
