OL,3,CCleaner rivers and tougher action for
OL,4,Cpolluters promised in industry shake-up
OL,6,F"This needs to be a wake-up for the
OL,7,Fwater industry and is an overdue
OL,8,Fopportunity to fix the problems of the
OL,9,Fpast and become a clean water abundant
OL,10,Fnation," he said. "Any investment in
OL,11,Fthe water system must work urgently to
OL,12,Frestore nature, support food
OL,13,Fproduction, improve climate resilience
OL,14,Fand deliver new housing and
OL,15,Finfrastructure as we protect the long-
OL,16,Fterm health of our rivers, seas and
OL,17,Fthe water that's essential to life."
